Claude-Copilot Plugin for Claude Code

This project is a Claude Code plugin that wraps the GitHub Copilot CLI
(https://github.com/features/copilot/cli) and was inspired by the architecture
of the OpenAI Codex plugin for Claude Code (openai/codex-plugin-cc).

Trademarks and product names mentioned ("GitHub Copilot", "Claude Code",
"Claude") belong to their respective owners. This project is not affiliated
with or endorsed by GitHub, OpenAI, or Anthropic.
